1.01	Torn_(online_game)	Torn (online game)	Torn, previously called Torn City, is a free, online text-based role-playing game created by British online gaming entrepreneur Joe Chedburn. The game was launched in 2004. Around 30,000+ people play daily, and over 1.6 million accounts exist in total. Torn is a virtual world based around gang violence. Like many RPGs, players start out at the bottom rung and make their way to the top by earning experience points. The game focuses on crimes and player versus player combat as a way of earning XP or experience points. The game, as of July, is 7 years old.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/57/Torncity.jpg/220px-Torncity.jpg
